Introduction
========

QCharType is a chinese character typing game designed to be played
without activating IME of user's operating system.

Building
========

After this source tree is obtained, do as the following:

  # Assume current dir is root of source tree
  cd ..
  mkdir build
  qmake ../QCharType  # ./QCharType/ contains source tree
  make
  cp -r ../QCharType/share ./share

If zh_TW translation is needed, run makeTranslation.sh in the source
tree right after 'make' command.

Running
========

After build as describe above, just type

  ./QCharType

in your build directory.

